Package ca.mymenuapp.ui.debug

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ContextualDebugActions.DebugAction<T extends android.view.View>  
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ContextualDebugActions
    Watches incoming and outgoing views to display context specific actions.
    DebugAppContainer
    An AppContainer for debug builds which wrap the content view with a sliding drawer on the right that holds all of the debug information and settings.
    HierarchyTreeChangeListener
    A hierarchy change listener which recursively monitors an entire tree of views.
    SocketActivityHierarchyServer
    This class can be used to enable the use of HierarchyViewer inside an application.
